rows.label: qst202001_msg001
rows.name:
Oh my... Well, this is a bit of 
a troublesome situation, isn't it?

rows.label: qst202001_msg003
rows.name:
You don't often see a Blade
wandering about on her own.
Where's your Driver?

rows.label: qst202001_msg004
rows.name:
My name is Musubi. As it happens,
I'm actually a Blade.

rows.label: qst202001_msg005
rows.name: Um, yeah, I literally just said that...

rows.label: qst202001_msg006
rows.name:
You seemed to be worrying about
something. Anything we can do?

rows.label: qst202001_msg007
rows.name:
Yes, well...I came here to do some
shopping, but they don't have what
I'm looking for in stock...

rows.label: qst202001_msg008
rows.name:
And since Superbia are regulating
what gets through to Gula...

rows.label: qst202001_msg009
rows.name:
there are a lot of products that don't
make it to the marketplace.

rows.label: qst202001_msg010
rows.name:
I know! Would you mind terribly picking
out some ingredients for me?

rows.label: qst202001_msg011
rows.name:
I would go myself, but I don't really
have the luxury of straying too far.

rows.label: qst202001_msg013
rows.name:
Sure, I don't mind. So what's this
fancy stuff you're after?

rows.label: qst202001_msg014
rows.name:
Oh, I'm not sure you could call it
fancy per se...

rows.label: qst202001_msg015
rows.name:
I'm looking for 5 clumps of Salty Soil,
8 portions of Gromrice, and 5 Ruby
Mangosteens.

rows.label: qst202001_msg016
rows.name:
I'm always in the area, so just come
back here when you're done.

rows.label: qst202001_msg017
rows.name:
Tora understand. Will be waiting here
too.
